{"tid":1784333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我識得有部份陰陽眼人士","createTime":"2019-12-15T15:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T15:02:39.000Z","uid":105340,"like":24,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ccb6b8aac6065cba1dfd94c8069fede53e302f1","tid":1784333,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"其實佢地見到落單 休班狗 背後好多鍾陰身跟住<br />\n佢地知道邊個係 便衣狗 <br />\n但真係唔可以鍾陰身知道陰陽眼手足見到佢地<br />\n仲有狗屋 其實 關公像果個關公真係走左啦<br />\n入面個神像被人奪舍了 好多冤死的魂  同妖怪係入面<br />\n尤其太子站 附近果個狗屋 <br />\n無咩師傅肯鎮佢地<br />\n就算肯 都會衰三世 禍及子孫<br />\n<br />\n我就信而D野<br />\n信不信就由你<br />\n反正我冇陰陽眼 都搵人落左部份狗降頭 ( 用自己壽命3年)<br />\n天理遁還<br />\n我相信 人在做 天在做<br />\n上帝都救唔到班狗"},{"pid":"63265c14173b72b16c61ea721f7651824413b14b","tid":1784333,"uid":192732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:04:59.000Z","msg":"想學iamgay? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2c2e585c1cb93486c6f2824d51ca00a209af9af","tid":1784333,"uid":33495,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"等鬼神不如自己做"},{"pid":"6bab4ce20f390a1a768c7a90f2186e08f0cde020","tid":1784333,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"iamgay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14595daf12cfda3f20dad880883eb45594a150d9","tid":1784333,"uid":288673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"信"},{"pid":"d63e14d311151f616805d9df5fc67c4c02d85b4a","tid":1784333,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bab4ce20f390a1a768c7a90f2186e08f0cde020","tid":1784333,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"iamgay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"邊位???"},{"pid":"23a5a5bba34b648356426dcd9eda7321a2d53dd3","tid":1784333,"uid":105340,"li